ast. – No chump love suckers', 'IMG_18_102_20.jpg', 'It''s a fact, do not get confused, everyone knows that true friends are few. – Walkin’ on down the road', 'IMG_19_102_21.jpg', 'I will do my best to relieve your pain. – Subway to Venus', 'IMG_20_102_23.jpg', 'Do not be afraid to show your friends that you are hurt inside, pain is part of life, do not hide it behind your false pride. – Knock me down', 'IMG_21_102_24.jpg', 'I am part of you and you are part of me. Because you left? – Knock me down', 'IMG_22_102_25.jpg', 'I have to kiss you goodbye. Goodbye my love, goodbye my love. I''m not alive. – Taste the pain', 'IMG_23_102_11.jpg', 'I do not want to feel what I felt that day, take me to the place I love. – Under the bridge', 'IMG_24_102_12.jpg', 'It is hard to believe that there is no one out there. It''s hard to believe that I''m so lonely. – Under the bridge', 'IMG_25_102_13.jpg', 'There are loves for which you can not fight. – Naked in the rain', 1),
